_sText: NAV FILE HERE: NAVFILE Hi there! Finally i finished this map. So there should'nt be major bugs. It's a big smokey city themed map with L-Train and subway station. There are 3 main routes to the bombsites. Terrorists must destroy the L-Train tracks or eliminate the Playground. Counter-terrorist have to defend the spots at all costs. Don't use snipers for more fun :D + changelogs Added bombsite B. Added 32-32 spawns. Added extra route to B. Added covers on streets(boxes,wrecks) Added HDR and soundscapes + volumetric fog. Added a noobroom for cheaters :D or annoying players. Credits: Thanks to Chizbone for making the advanced nav file. Thanks to Nauz for the palm model. Thanks to tazzz for helping with major bugs and fixing some errors. Enjoy (and don't forget to give me a hi5 :) )
